text: Sona Mikyskova (born 2 May 1989) is a Czech volleyball player. She played at the 2014 FIVB World Grand Prix, 2015 FIVB World Grand Prix, and 2016 FIVB World Grand Prix. She played for Pays d'Aix Venelles Volley-Ball and WVC Dynamo Kazan. == References == Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Czech volleyball players
